<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF7C6AC3FF8E9D9F1F46B76E" pageId="135" pageNumber="895" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF7C6AC3FF8E9D9F1F46B76E" blockId="135.[112,1319,2974,3172]" pageId="135" pageNumber="895">
Specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF7C6AC3FEBB9D9F1FC3B0D5" authorityName="Peters" authorityYear="1866" box="[327,451,3014,3047]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="135" pageNumber="895" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="jagorii">P. jagorii</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF7C6AC3FDD89D9F1C65B0D5" box="[548,613,3014,3047]" name="Laos" pageId="135" pageNumber="895">Laos</collectingCountry>
are apparently slightly smaller than elsewhere and might be a distinct taxon. Up to three subspecies (
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF7C6AC3FC639DB41DF8B73C" authorityName="Peters" authorityYear="1866" box="[927,1016,3053,3086]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="135" pageNumber="895" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="jagorii">jagorii</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF7C6AC3FBFA9DB41A77B73C" authorityName="Chasen" authorityYear="1939" box="[1030,1143,3053,3086]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glischropus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="135" pageNumber="895" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="javanus">javanus</taxonomicName>
, and rapax) have been recognized, but additional studies are needed to determine their validity. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF7C6AC3F82B977517F1BAD4" pageId="135" pageNumber="895" type="distribution">
<caption id="90EB6676FF7C6AC3F82B977517F1BAD4" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6398434" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6398434" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6398434/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="135" pageNumber="895" targetBox="[1392,1983,303,717]" targetPageId="135">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF7C6AC3F82B977517F1BAD4" blockId="135.[2006,2599,300,722]" pageId="135" pageNumber="895">
